snippet.title: PC Engine Longplay [161] TaleSpin
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by NPI

Isn't it weird that Baloo from The Jungle Book can fly a plane all of a sudden. Nevermind. This game is also a very hard one, as you dont get energy power ups I died once but I respawned quickly and it didn't affect the longplay very much. You might also have some special moves in this game that I wasn't aware of. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
